<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=11-011103478.pdf">Read the Charge</a><br/>
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Thur, Sept 22, 2011</strong><br/>
HUD has charged owners of an apartment complex in La Crosse, WI with discrimination based on race.<br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=11-051102008.PDF">Read the Charge</a><br/>
&nbsp; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/HUD?src=/press/press_releases_media_advisories/2011/HUDNo.11-228">Read the Press Release</a></li>
<li><strong>Wed, Sept 21, 2011</strong><br/>
HUD has charged a Minnesota landlord with discrimination on the basis of disability .<br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=11-051104468.pdf">Read the Charge</a><br/>
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Wed, Sept 16, 2011</strong><br/>
HUD has charged an owners cooperative on Long Island, New York with discrimination based on disability.<br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=11-020901408.pdf">Read the Charge</a><br/>
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Tuesday, Sept 15, 2011</strong><br/>
HUD has charged the owner and manager of Breckenridge Plaza Apartments in Phoenixville, PA, with violating the Fair Housing Act by discriminating against families with children.<br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=11-031100278.PDF">Read the Charge</a><br/>
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Tuesday, Sept 13, 2011</strong><br/>
HUD on behalf of the Fair Housing Council of Suburban Philadelphia v. Young Kim, Kwang Kim, and Margaret Kim.<br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=11-031102128.PDF">Read the Charge</a><br/>
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Friday, Sept 02, 2011</strong><br/>
HUD has charged a Wisconsin property owner with discrimination based on sex and familial status.<br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=051103198.pdf">Read the Charge</a><br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/HUD?src=/press/press_releases_media_advisories/2011/HUDNo.11-207 ">Read the Press Release</a><br/>
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Thursday, Sept 01, 2011</strong><br/>
HUD charges the City of Santa Rosa and a Homeowners Association with discrimination against families what children.<br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=090914548.pdf">Read the Charge</a><br/>
&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Thursday, Sept 01, 2011</strong><br/>
HUD has charged real estate broker in Mississippi with housing discrimination against an African-American family.<br/>
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120402122117/http://portal.hud.gov/hudportal/documents/huddoc?id=040608988.PDF">Read the Charge</a><br/>
